{"tid":1366784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港01：【光復元朗】再申不反對通知書　申請人：提第二方案免周六大混亂","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:52:55.000Z","uid":246671,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87b00876b968d471021a745834831210d13f9097","tid":1366784,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"有網民發起於周六（27日）舉行光復元朗遊行，抗議7.21元朗發生的無差別襲擊事件，早前元朗居民鍾健平代為申請不反對通知書，但被警方以擔心衝突構成危險、拒絕更改遊行路線等五項原因為由發出反對通知書。今日（26日）有市民自發再次為光復元朗申請不反對通知書，建議路線由元朗西鐵站H出口出發，沿鳳翔街、合益路、教育路，經水邊圍至朗屏西鐵站解散，時間同樣為下午三時集合，三時半起步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/356503/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%86%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%8F%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%85%8D%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F356503%2F%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2585%258D%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9431d9b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/356503/%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%86%8D%E7%94%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%8F%90%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%85%8D%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82</a>"},{"pid":"fe0a803358269225e51e2e73069021013635fa78","tid":1366784,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a29fd5f27fd6f92b97c6fbfc03e8f3499801b8